Rom updater-script for B2G

To create the b2g rom:
1. open the Makefile
2. change B2G to the path of your (new)B2G build directory
3. change DEVICE to your device name
4. make
5. The output will be in rom_out/b2g.zip

To flash your new rom:
1. You need to have clockworkmod recovery installed
2. Boot into recovery mode by simultaneously pressing volume up, home and power keys
3. Select install from zip file
4. Select b2g.rom
5. Nait till installation completes
6. Now reboot
7. Enjoy!!

Warning: Still in alpha stage. We are not responsible if you brick you mobile. We ourselves have not successfully flashed it :)
